{
  "chapter": 226,
  "chapter_summary": "第226章《纠缠不休》讲述寇仲与徐子陵乘船北上，途中在梁都遭遇彭梁会陈家风等人。寇仲进城采购时与陈家风交谈，得知梁都因窦建德进攻而防守空虚，宇文化及的军队也在附近活动。与此同时，徐子陵在船上发现婠婠潜入，两人对峙。婠婠透露阴癸派要彻底解决他们，边不负也现身。徐子陵机智逃脱，但船只被劫。寇仲及时赶到，与婠婠对峙。最终两人与陈家风等人会合，得知契丹人组成东海盟在沿海劫掠。众人决定一起前往江都。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们从南方出发时，好像天下都给踩在脚下的样子，岂知波折重重，志复等三人惨遭不幸，玉成则不知所踪，我们现更为势所迫，要折返南方，关中过门不入，想想便教人颓然若失。\n\n",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "志复三人的仇我们必定要报的，大丈夫恩怨分明，阴癸派手段如此凶残可恶，终有日我们会将它连根拔起，令她们永不能再害人。\n\n",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了宇文化及外，现时和我们仇恨最深的就是阴癸派，血债必须血偿，何况就算我们肯忍气吞声，涫妖女和祝妖妇也绝不肯放过我们。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这亦是我肯陪你去江都的原因，否则我会立即赶往巴陵接素姐母子。\n\n我到现在仍不明白为何老爹肯与虎谋皮，和阴癸派合作去打天下，其中定有些我们尚未知道的原由。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "管她娘的那么多！明天我们转入通济渠后，便日夜兼程赶赴江都。\n\n不过可要补充乾粮食水，因为至少也再要三天三夜，才可抵达江都。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我总有些不祥的预感，这一程未必会那么顺利。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们有那天是平安无事的？\n\n谁不怕死，就放马过来吧！哈！学而后知不足，我也要拿鲁大爷的宝笈出来下点苦功。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟该我去用功了，交给你掌舟才是",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟彭梁会智堂香主陈家风，请问这位好汉贵姓大名，来自何乡何县？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟傅仁，刚在东都做完买卖，现在赶回江都。\n\n哈！泊码头当然有泊码头的规矩，小弟该向贵会缴纳多少银两，请陈香主赐示。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看傅兄神采飞扬的样子，定是捞足了油水，傅兄这艘船也是最上等的货式，最奇怪是傅兄似乎只有一名伙计在船上。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先礼后兵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陈兄说得好。小弟既敢和我那个兄弟驾着一条上价船走南闯北，当然是有点凭恃。\n\n不过念在大家都是江湖同道，加上我们又很尊敬'鬼爪'聂敬他老人家，且与贵帮三当家'艳娘子'任媚媚有点交情，才依规矩办事，陈兄该明白小弟的意思吧！\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请问傅兄是那条线上的朋友？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真人不露相，露相非真人，陈兄若肯卖个交情，便不要查根究底，就当没见过小弟吧。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭梁会看来已控制了这截水道，只不知他们现在归附何方？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是任媚媚的手下，照计不是投向徐圆朗，就该是李子通。\n\n嘿！应不会是宇文化及吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我负责入城采购，你可不要让人把船抢去。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若来的是祝玉妍、婠婠之流，你可勿要怨我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打仗真害人不浅，好好一个繁华都会，变成这个样子。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟发生甚么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这真是一言难尽，若你早来数天，便可看到这里以千万计的人挤得道路水泄不通，哭喊震天，四散逃命的可怕情景。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这城本是何方拥有？又是谁要来攻城呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这城已历经数手，最后一手是徐圆朗，只是好景不常，最近因窦建德挥军渡河，攻打徐圆朗的根据地城任，徐圆朗于是仓卒抽调梁都军队往援，致梁都防守薄弱，最后连那数百守军都溜掉，使梁都变成一座没人管没人理的城市。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "窦建德那么可怕吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "窦建德当然不可怕，论声誉他要比徐圆朗好得多，但宇文化及的狗腿贼兵，却比阎皇勾命的鬼差更骇人。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当日宇文化及率兵由江都北返，去到那里便抢到那里，残害百姓，奸淫妇女，所以风声传来，人人都争相躲往附近乡间避难。\n\n唉！这年头要走都不容易，处处都在打仗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宇文化及会否亲来呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个便没人知道，我们是做一日和尚撞一日钟，形势不对便溜之大吉，若傅兄不介意，可否仗义送我们到江都去？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们要到江都还不容易吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你根本不熟悉江都的情况，竟不知李子通在河渠重重设关，除非是和他们有关系的船只，其他一概不准驶往江都，否则我何用求你。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我确是不知江都的情况，皆因久未回去，但却非和李子通没有关系，陈兄可以放心。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傅兄和李子通有甚么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们彭梁会能名列八帮十会之一，该不会是省油灯，为何不乘机把梁都接收过来，完全只是一副任人打不还手的样儿？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非看出傅兄非是平凡之辈，小弟也懒得和你说这么多话。\n\n今时已不同往日，当年昏君被杀，我们在聂帮主的统领下。\n\n一举取下彭城和梁都附近的四十多个乡镇，本以为可据地称霸，大有作为。\n\n岂知先后败于宇文化及和徐圆朗手上，最近连彭城都给蛮贼攻陷，我们彭梁会已是名存实亡，连会主在那里都不清楚。\n\n",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "甚么蛮贼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n徐子陵皱眉道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n婠婠秀眉轻蹙的不悦道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n徐子陵哑然失笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n忽地脸色一变，撞破舱顶，来到船只的上空。\n\n系舟的索子已被绷断，船只正移离岸旁，顺水流下。\n\n婠婠的天魔劲正自脚下攻至。\n\n陈家风愤然道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n寇仲愕然道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n陈家风道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n旋又叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_bu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "边不负",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n这时陈家风才和一众大汉赶至，人人脸露祟慕尊敬之色。\n\n寇仲没好气的扫了他们一眼，道：",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n陈家风尴尬的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n徐子陵叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n陈家风低声问道：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n寇仲点头应是。\n\n陈家风露出佩服至五体投地的神色，道：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n徐子陵失笑道：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n陈家风身后一名汉子竖起拇指道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n寇仲道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n陈家风喜道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 226,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    }
  ],
